# Contributing & Setup Guide

This rule provides quick instructions for setting up the development environment and contributing to AskAI.

## Setup

1. Clone the repository:
   ```sh
   git clone https://github.com/YOUR-USERNAME/AskAI.git
   cd AskAI
   ```
2. Create a `.env` file in `src/Core`:
   ```env
   OPENAI_API_KEY=your-key-here
   ```
3. Build and run the application:
   ```sh
   dotnet run --project src/UI/UI.csproj
   ```

## Contributing

- Press <kbd>Alt</kbd>+<kbd>Space</kbd> to open the overlay and verify changes.
- Ensure code follows C# conventions.
- Add tests to the `tests` directory.
- Submit PRs against the `main` branch.

